<P>A SERMON Preach'd before the ARCHBISHOP, Bi&s;hops, and Clergy, OF THE <HI>Province of CANTERBURY</HI> MET IN CONVOCATION At the Cathedral Church of St. <HI>Paul,</HI> on <HI>Monday, February</HI> 10. 1700.</P>
<P>By <HI>W. HAYLEY,</HI> D.D. Dean of <HI>Chiche&s;ter.</HI></P>
<P>Publi&s;hed by Command of His Grace the Archbi&s;hop of <HI>Canterbury.</HI></P>
<P>Done into <HI>Engli&s;h</HI> from the <HI>Latin</HI> Original, By <HI>W. JONES,</HI> A.B.</P>
<P><HI>LONDON,</HI> Printed for <HI>J. Ton&s;on,</HI> under <HI>Gray</HI>'s-Inn-Gate, in <HI>Gray</HI>'s-Inn-Lane. MDCCI.</P>
